> Phobia heard the signal, another predacon. He'd try to remember, if he had
> his ship he wouldn't have to worry about it, he could have the ship keep
> track of these things but alas he'd have to rely on his wits and charm to
> see his group through these things.
>
> OOC they're all in trouble.
>

Thrash grumbled as all his signal got in return was static his form shifting
becoming half the great white shark but his fins were replaced with small
boosters and a section of his belly opened revealing an anti grav device.
Hovering several feet from the ground the shark bot tore into the forest,
his sharp fins and chomping teeth whittling away the trees in his way as he
moved toward where the original signature had been...
